query:
ALTER TABLE importedFiles 
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS schemaVersion VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT '2.0.0',
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS pageCount INT,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS isTextExtractable BOOLEAN,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS isScannedDocument BOOLEAN,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS vesselDataCompleteness DECIMAL(5,2),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS tmlDataCompleteness DECIMAL(5,2),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS physicalValidationPassRate DECIMAL(5,2),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS confidenceScoreAverage DECIMAL(3,2),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS overallQuality ENUM('complete', 'partial', 'needs_review', 'failed');
